{"tid":2175894,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蘋果A1: 警謊竄改7.21 歷史","createTime":"2020-08-26T18:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T20:16:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"888c6e435bba4416ec132c658600abd4c854400f","tid":2175894,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/118075299_10159392642787448_4291500934341156093_o.png?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=09wsOBq6WHkAX8QWwTR&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=e780f4a65988c6650e1acd48ced97ba9&amp;oe=5F6C5988\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F118075299_10159392642787448_4291500934341156093_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3D09wsOBq6WHkAX8QWwTR%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3De780f4a65988c6650e1acd48ced97ba9%26oe%3D5F6C5988&h=2bf8c8fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【#A1頭條】警方昨晨以7 月21 日在港鐵元朗站參與暴動為由，拘捕一直要求追查事件真相的民主黨立法會議員林卓廷，令原告變被告，再把 13 名當晚在場面對白衣人恐襲威嚇的人士以同樣罪名拘捕。新界北總區刑事總部高級警司陳天柱交代案件時化身「港版袁木」，把警察遲到 39分鐘改稱為 18 分鐘；白衣人早有預謀的無差別襲擊，更被定性為不同派別人士的對峙及聚集，企圖竄改7.21 歷史。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.170516952447/10159392642782448/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fphotos%2Fa.170516952447%2F10159392642782448%2F&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatmCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=3f3fff30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.170516952447/10159392642782448/</a>"},{"pid":"579839bbfc74c87c5610dfdb43eec0ce8ee8ebee","tid":2175894,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f